<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6646> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6646" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/3> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "No title preserved. Author of a bill to regulate the selection of Vestal Virgins by the Pontifex Maximus (Gell. 1.12.10-12). His date may be earlier than that of the moneyer L. Papius (6), who appears to refer to some law, but Berger (RE, Supb. 7.402) refers this law to C. Papius (5), Tr. Pl. in 65." .
